From 16e0941b5778050adc5b6082d141f2feacaa4137 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 10 Nov 2025 11:08:48 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Modernize Cordova demo: Update dependencies and fix
 critical bugs
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Dependencies:
- Update to cordova-plugin-audioinput v2.0.0
- Update cordova-android to ^13.0.0 (from 7.0.0)
- Update cordova-ios to ^7.1.0 (from 4.5.4)
- Update cordova-plugin-file to ^8.0.0
- Remove deprecated cordova-plugin-compat
- Remove deprecated cordova-plugin-splashscreen

Bug Fixes:
- Fix memory leak in events-demo.js (unbounded audioDataQueue)
  * Add maxQueueSize limit (100 chunks)
  * Implement queue overflow handling
- Fix memory leak in file-demo.js (unbounded audioDataBuffer)
  * Add maxBufferSize limit (5 minutes of audio)
  * Auto-stop when limit reached
- Fix typos: "recieved" → "received" in all error handlers
- Reset audioDataBuffer on new recording start

Improvements:
- Enhanced CSS with modern styling
  * Loading spinner animations
  * Button press feedback
  * Color-coded status messages (error/success/warning)
  * Improved timer display
  * Recording indicator with pulse animation
  * Audio level meter styling
  * Better recording list links
- Better visual feedback
- Improved mobile responsiveness
